{title: Grid Section}
{key: G}
{tempo: 120}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Playing through the [C]grid
[D]Rhythm pattern [G]here
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_grid}
| G  . . . | C  . . . | D  . . . | G  . . . |
| G  . . . | C  . . . | D  . . . | G  . . . |
| Em . . . | C  . . . | D  . . . | G  . . . |
| Em . . . | C  . . . | D  . D . | G  . . . |
{end_of_grid}

{comment: Play grid pattern twice}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Follow the [G]grid
[D]Feel the [G]beat
[C]Every [G]measure
[D]Nice and [G]neat
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_grid: Outro}
| G  . . . | C  . . . |
| D  . . . | G  . . . |
{end_of_grid}
